Help_Text_HowToUseMoveOutsideOfBattle::
	.string "{CIRCLE_1} Open the Menu.\n"
	.string "{CIRCLE_2} Select “Pokémon.”\n"
	.string "{CIRCLE_3} Select a Pokémon that knows an\n"
